snippet.textDisplay: Quality of the song aside I don't like this trend of what can rightly be called nepotism in CS. How do 3 persons get a chance without even trying their hand at singing independently and trying to win fans before being given a chance here ? This is an elite platform, and while giving chances to talents like Aima, Momina and some others is fine, star-kids come with a certain baggage and they need to relieve themselves of it first by doing some stuff outside CS. I was hoping this trend would be heavily criticised but turns out we criticise only when its cricket or politics.
